      "title": "Ranil takes oath as Acting President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has been sworn in as the Acting President. Following the resignation of the President, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe was sworn in as the Acting President in accordance with the provisions of the Constitution.",
        "The new President is scheduled to be elected on the 20th by a majority vote in the Parliament."
